<h1>Goals</h1>
<ul>
<li>Allow practical one-to-many publishing of information
<li>Provide reasonable anonymity for producers and consumers of 
information
<li>Provide deniability for operators of nodes in the network
<li>Rely on no centralized control or network administration
<li>Be scalable from tens to hundreds of thousands of users
<li>Be robust against node failure or malicious attack
</ul>
